con:config.con:query: select distinct t.[TBL_CDWRD], m.Record_Key, m.WGP_ID_NBR,sli.[SLI_SHP_TAG] from Legacy.M204_WGP m left outer join Legacy.M204_SLI sli on sli.[SLI_SHP_TAG] = m.[WGP_SHP_TAG ] left outer join Legacy.M204_TBL t on t.[TBL_CDWRD]=sli.[SLI_BCW] where (m.WGP_ID_NBR = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}' and t.[TBL_CDWRD]= 'NTFY' and t.RECTYPE='TBL11.BASE' and sli.[sli_bcw] is not null) order by t.[TBL_CDWRD] asc

select s.Shipment_Key ,ai.Accessorial_Item_CD, s.PRO_NB, s.WGP_Record_Key from SHIP.Shipment s left outer join [SHIP].[BOL_Accessorial_Item_VW] bai on (bai.[Shipment_KEY] = s.[Shipment_KEY]) left outer join [SHIP].[Accessorial_Item_VW] ai on (ai.[Accessorial_Item_KEY] = bai.[Accessorial_Item_KEY]) where s.PRO_NB = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}' and ai.Accessorial_Item_CD = 'NTFY' and ai.Accessorial_Item_CD is not null order by s.PRO_NB desc, ai.Accessorial_Item_CD asc
